{"tid":1639123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] Feel到開始有d人覺得攰，我提返你一次721發生左咩事","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:14:18.000Z","uid":76944,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b778ac02ff41b372d64cb7eece1f831016139a8d","tid":1639123,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"咁我提你一次呢個政府同黑警係點對佢既市民<br />\n<br />\n我唔會洗版，只會同你講多次721<br />\n<br />\n721 : 黑警事前已知有鄉黑出離，同鄉黑勾結，默許佢地出離打人，特登唔調配警隊，事後當晚黑警係白衣人身邊行過，一個人都唔拉<br />\n<br />\n香港市民比人打到皮開肉綻<br />\n<br />\n當晚凌晨4點，林鄭月娥出離鬧人塗污國徽，一句關心過香港市民既說話都無講過，視國徽多過人命<br />\n<br />\n至今無警察因此停職，無為此道歉，你<br />\n<br />\n~<br />\n<br />\n我知人係有惰性，但你唔係已經嬲完下嘩。<br />\n<br />\n大家記住而家係場戰爭，你停落離，人地就會攻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ad8354c1625470522447608dcf0a2cf55ec89be7","tid":1639123,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16befc363068584caf369c359adb972b1dc90b0","tid":1639123,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"全部同我出返離"},{"pid":"acfdc76dd71e3fc150761edcdafa3590c149cbb2","tid":1639123,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"唔係咁就算下嘩"},{"pid":"efcb9b9627c10f9d32fb9f29ab6fdb6946a14b4f","tid":1639123,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"緊急 希望有4000和理非幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638741</a>"},{"pid":"0e8ed0547e83a1bd832dcedf41e26af1152c1f36","tid":1639123,"uid":215755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:56